turned down us having tactical nuclear weapons 
along with Admiral Radford the chairman of the

04:32.495 --> 04:40.425
Joint Chiefs. So Senator Scoop Jackson who is a 
magnificent individual and a knowing man and who

04:42.428 --> 05:01.472
believes in the defense of the free world in the 
United States he was chairman of the Joint he was

04:42.428 --> 05:01.472
chairman of the subcommittee for military 
application on the Joint Committee on Atomic

05:01.705 --> 05:09.553
Energy. It was a joint committee in those days 
