otherwise, then you never have to worry about 
tomorrow. You don't have to worry about what you

22:05.518 --> 22:07.642
said today. You never have to do that. You don't 
have to have a long memory. Yes, but honesty is one

22:11.908 --> 22:16.135
thing, and politics is something entirely 
different at times. That's true. And you're

22:17.297 --> 22:20.702
dealing now, and not in the military sphere— but 
